description: The underlying index seeks to provide exposure to innovative companies by investing in the equities of U.S. large cap companies that have high research and development (“R&D”) spending. The fund invests, under normal circumstances, at least 80% of its net assets, plus the amount of any borrowings for investment purposes, in the investments included in its underlying index. The fund is non-diversified.
name: NYLI U.S. Large Cap R&D Leaders ETF
